[Thanks to Marco for this. It is good to see a country taking dengue
control seriously. Spraying against mosquitoes can only reduce the
problem; destroying breeding places around & inside houses eliminates
it. Cuba has done that more than once; but vigilance must be
maintained against reimportation of the mosquito. - Mod.JW
